Package: piappt
Title: Lightweight Helpers for Slide-Master PowerPoint Generation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Minimal helper functions for generating PowerPoint decks from an
    existing slide master. Includes a front-page title slide helper and a
    primary content slide workflow for injecting charts, titles, and bullet
    points into named placeholders.
